    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This technique allows the user to entrap much larger creatures than Suishō Rō no Jutsu , but at the expense of the lethality. A creature that fails its save is trapped within an area of crystal, unable to perform any abilities or techniques that requires mobility or hand seals. The prison has a hardness of 10 and 40 hit points. A trapped creature can attempt to shatter the crystal with a Strength Check DC (35).</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Requires:</b> Shoton Gokakuro (3)(t)</p>\n",
